Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe in all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it because it's quiet in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel comfortable just sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to examine the guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Each day, I linger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,While my heart wanders day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I yearn to find my destined companion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So my heart will stop wandering
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I long for the day you suddenly come
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And accept me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And assure me the person I'm eyeing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That all of your promises will last forever
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So many expectations, so many dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart worries about so many things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there wasn't much hope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Having hope would be enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To look forward to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my heartfelt desire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes, why would I deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cornea has been damaged. - Will I get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your vision has been impaired, but there's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't see. - The cornea can be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. - Will I go blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, I'm a policeman. Can you remember the face of the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I'm really scared. - Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fought them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I drive you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I listen to you sing every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to you sing all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like we've become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your eyes have been damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've wanted to help, but never had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone in the world is a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me help just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave once I see that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That cat is always coming in and tearing up my clothes. It's a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you switch the light off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a shadow. It wasn't this bad last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I could see contours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to leave the light on. I feel safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just looking at the scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bloodstain, right? I can't wash it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who injured my eyes left this scarf behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget him for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get you a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. - No, let me. You helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not listen to some music?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Each day, I linger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart wanders day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I yearn to find my destined companion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So my heart will stop wandering
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I long for the day you suddenly come
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And accept me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And assure me the person I'm eyeing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That all of your promises will last forever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So many expectations, so many dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Eagle, you're too earnest. It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One look at you, and they'll know you're a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile. Smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You look like a police inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chang, stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is like a mad dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because he's crazy doesn't mean you have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to come out of this alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Hung, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this? - He's one of my boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Brother Hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brother Hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't our first transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen him somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's $20,000 HK.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After I've seen the merchandise, I'll give you the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here? - Nothing, sir. We're just chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the suitcase for me. Open the suitcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did this cop show up? - It's a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Hung! On my life, he's not a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way! - Trust me! He's not cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen him in a police station!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsang Yeh! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A mad dog. He's really is a mad dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish that sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Li, the suspect Wong Hung was holding a hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the tram was filled with passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't even sure where the suspect was, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. - On what basis did you fire your gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you consider the passengers' safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you issue a warning before firing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The hostage had a heart problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Her family stated that you fired without warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was literally frightened to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They insist on pursuing the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have known that she had a heart problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been investigating Wong Hung for six or seven months.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mentally unstable and has homicidal tendencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather I'd waited until he killed the hostage before I fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The cop that Wong Hung killed, was his death in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can his family complain to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Write up whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I get charges filed against me on whatever cases I work anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my badge, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your hand had healed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No plans to go to physio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A shooter without two able hands is like a cripple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I got back into the practice, I'll never be as good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Wong Dung-Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He has contacts with Central and South American drug lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he a target? - Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want $1.5 million HK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a bit high?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, you'll never see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Somebody wants him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These are unregistered and don't have serial numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Very clean. The police won't be able to trace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets have been altered the way you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy to pick up, difficult to put down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you agree to do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny's cornea isn't transparent anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't get a transplant soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then she may go blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a cornea bank in Hong Kong,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately it's out of stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if someone was willing to donate a cornea,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there's already a waiting list with several hundred people on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,CHURCH OF SALVATION
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go away for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back and take you to America and we'll get your eyes healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the Dragon Boat Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be many important government officials and other VIPs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...in attendance at the Painting The Dragon's Eyes ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The information you have been given...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...pertains to the person that you're assigned to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stay alert and be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this scum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...needs our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the Painting The Dragon's Eyes ceremony is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Would all the competing dragon boats please gather in front of the podium.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're fortunate to have the chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Dung-Yu Group with us, Mr. Dung-Yu Wong;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the Legco councilman, Mr. Si-Ming Chow;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Kong chairman of the Rotary Club, Mr. Gwok-Wah Chu;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,president of the Professional Women's Association, Ms. Mung-Chu Lee Lam;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and many other VIPs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,many of whom are movie stars and pop idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After the ceremony, the final match of the dragon boat race will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We hope all athletes will try their best! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss! - Mr. Wong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.89,0:24:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wong, please begin painting. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.66,0:26:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chow, are you okay? - What's his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.21,0:26:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cover him up. Don't alarm the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All units! There's been a shooting on the VIP podium.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.01,0:26:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wong Dung-Yu has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.35,0:26:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets came from the direction of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.19,0:26:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The murderer is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.59,0:26:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All units! Begin searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.63,0:26:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop and interrogate anyone who looks suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.20,0:26:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wong just fainted. It's nothing. - Oh, good. He just fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go on with the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.40,0:27:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsang Yeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.94,0:28:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.53,0:30:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsang Yeh! There's an explosion over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.97,0:30:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.27,0:30:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! Let's go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.92,0:30:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the guy! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.23,0:31:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.01,0:32:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.01,0:32:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.99,0:32:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's down there! Follow him! Quickly! - Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.70,0:32:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of any hospitals around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.50,0:32:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's where he's heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.77,0:32:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to discard the girl on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.42,0:33:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse, where's the emergency room?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.89,0:33:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.30,0:33:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.83,0:33:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.13,0:33:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us. Measure her blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.93,0:33:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.13,0:33:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help her regain consciousness as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.84,0:33:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the EKG heart monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.01,0:33:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her condition? Is her pulse and blood pressure normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.85,0:33:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is very weak and the blood pressure is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.12,0:33:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a man carrying a little girl come through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.56,0:33:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the casualty room. - Be on the lookout for anyone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.79,0:33:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what's your relationship to the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.66,0:33:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she get injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.69,0:33:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.40,0:33:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.43,0:33:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to register your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.70,0:33:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.85,0:34:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police. Just continue your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.58,0:34:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone stay calm and carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.76,0:34:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore them. Focus on the girl. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.60,0:34:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother the doctors. Lower your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.14,0:35:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here! - Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.41,0:35:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? - Someone fired a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.01,0:35:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? - Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.81,0:35:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.42,0:35:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.04,0:35:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.21,0:35:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you got? - Not much, Chief Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.08,0:35:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the suspect, but he escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.58,0:35:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you always operated on intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.25,0:35:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people want to see me fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.05,0:35:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm betting that I'll win this case, not lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.86,0:35:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do well, it benefits both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.06,0:36:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to have another chance like this in your entire career.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.49,0:36:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on a good show, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.86,0:36:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Inspector Dou, I don't know how to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.60,0:36:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll try my best to catch the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.87,0:36:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get promoted, don't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.08,0:36:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, draw him as I describe him. Just try to draw his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.29,0:36:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In his thirties with some crow's feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.39,0:36:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a manly air about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.96,0:36:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bit different from your average murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.90,0:36:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very calm, quite intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.23,0:36:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes are very alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.30,0:36:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.11,0:36:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.36,0:37:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. - It's Ah Jong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.96,0:37:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong? Why haven't you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.00,0:37:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.23,0:37:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.90,0:37:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.30,0:37:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll bring it over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.65,0:38:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wong, you should have let me handle Ah Jong today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.42,0:38:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have sent people to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.19,0:38:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he reveals my identity? - He's not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.19,0:38:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never trusted anyone in this line of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.66,0:38:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Including you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very clear on triad rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.60,0:38:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his manager. I'll deal with the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.77,0:38:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the rules, just the methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.84,0:38:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His identity has been exposed, and I want him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.61,0:38:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the boss, and I can play this game however I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.01,0:38:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll let you deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.41,0:38:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can't handle him, I'll deal with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.38,0:38:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, you're on my payroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.44,0:39:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be linked with an old case.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.41,0:39:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Six months ago, there was some unrest among the triads.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.51,0:39:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wong Dung-Yu's triad brother, Jeung Wan, was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.71,0:39:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A female singer got her eyes injured in the crossfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.48,0:39:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The shooter has yet to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.62,0:39:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the singer's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.86,0:39:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.42,0:39:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she almost lost her sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.20,0:39:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Every shot takes a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.47,0:39:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no ordinary assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.04,0:39:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be looking for the same man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.08,0:39:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If my intuition is correct, he's not a cold-blooded killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.15,0:39:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His every shot takes a life and he's not cold-blooded?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.68,0:39:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He risked his life to take that little girl to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.76,0:39:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's the man who injured the singer...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll still be in touch with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.43,0:40:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep myself drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.10,0:40:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend to be
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.61,0:40:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.68,0:40:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will not shed my tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.02,0:40:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! - Miss, you've made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.72,0:40:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I can't see very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.06,0:40:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mistook you for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.33,0:40:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That song is very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.37,0:40:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you sing it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.03,0:40:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I only sing it for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.54,0:40:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.87,0:40:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You sing the song with such feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.34,0:40:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel I'm getting to know your friend just by listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.41,0:40:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate that he's not here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.02,0:40:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever he is, he's going to miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.07,0:41:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.86,0:42:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.93,0:42:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.70,0:42:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.37,0:42:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In our line of work, it's sometimes difficult to trust even a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.38,0:42:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they know where I was getting off the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.12,0:42:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was driving the getaway car to the pier, I was followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.92,0:42:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.39,0:42:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.59,0:42:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why even ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.36,0:42:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.43,0:42:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run away when you had a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.40,0:42:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't been given my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.03,0:44:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.43,0:44:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't compromised your identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.43,0:45:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't have needed to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.03,0:45:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll repeat my question. Who's trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.28,0:45:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not sure if there are any bullets left.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.88,0:45:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember? I always save the last bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.89,0:45:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Either to kill someone else or kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.59,0:45:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wong Hoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.73,0:45:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wong Dung-Yu's nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.26,0:45:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.46,0:45:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who wanted you to kill his uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.40,0:46:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really have only one bullet left?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.31,0:46:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.72,0:46:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for sparing my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.79,0:46:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.02,0:46:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been put into a situation where there are no other choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.39,0:46:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.43,0:46:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.34,0:46:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Li, it's not exactly a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.09,0:47:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,'FLOAT' CHAN GU FONG
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.44,0:47:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.47,0:47:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't just be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.74,0:47:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that drawing and show it around to the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.31,0:47:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.95,0:47:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And accept me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.45,0:47:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And assure me the person I'm eyeing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.32,0:47:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That all of your promises will last forever
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.36,0:47:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So many expectations, so many dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.10,0:47:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart worries about so many things
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.21,0:48:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there wasn't much hope
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.15,0:48:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Having hope would be enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.85,0:48:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To look forward to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.86,0:48:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my heartfelt desire
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.26,0:48:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes, why would I deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.63,0:48:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you were right! I checked with the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.80,0:48:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He really has...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.18,0:48:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you going crazy or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.41,0:49:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.88,0:49:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.52,0:49:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get your medicine first.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.92,0:49:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going to take you somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.25,0:49:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.12,0:49:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving to less polluted surroundings would be better for your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.29,0:49:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.86,0:49:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be ideal if I could move close to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.93,0:49:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see the sea and the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.67,0:49:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.23,0:49:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you pack first?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.47,0:49:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.14,0:49:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.12,0:49:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run away when you had a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.52,0:49:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.37,0:50:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're the new garbage man?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.44,0:50:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, grandma. - You're so negligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.91,0:50:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fire escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.78,0:50:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're throwing the trash everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.15,0:50:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry, sorry. - If we're trapped by a fire, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.32,0:50:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You better move it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.12,0:50:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've paid my building maintenance fees. You're so lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.95,0:50:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reporting you to the main office. - I'm moving it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.76,0:50:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Okay, okay. - You'd better move it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.72,0:50:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mature adult and you're so lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.76,0:50:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So dirty! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.96,0:51:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong. Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.56,0:51:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.07,0:51:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought a friend home?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.37,0:51:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's a soccer buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.17,0:51:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've played soccer since we were children living in the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.98,0:51:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.48,0:51:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B. Shrimp Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.38,0:51:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You were called Shrimp Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.25,0:51:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.25,0:51:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both happy that we met up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.49,0:51:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.29,0:51:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you happy about seeing your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.56,0:51:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He gives out negative vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.83,0:51:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been following me around like a vengeful spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.43,0:51:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be following you around much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.06,0:51:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I pour you two some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.17,0:51:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. - No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.23,0:51:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.27,0:51:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to burn yourself. - Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.67,0:51:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm smart. I won't burn myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.41,0:51:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong, why don't you entertain Small B and take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.14,0:51:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a seat, Small B.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.48,0:51:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Shrimp Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.48,0:51:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, do you watch the people who throw out the trash every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.22,0:52:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, someone gave me $1,000 HK to chat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.26,0:52:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sir, we haven't finished chatting yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.99,0:52:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's talk some more before you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.46,0:52:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose this match. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.03,0:52:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who's going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.66,0:52:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who misses every time you're in front of the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.27,0:52:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. I have the best forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.87,0:52:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity that your forward is lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.48,0:52:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you always this earnest?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.98,0:52:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.45,0:52:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't take things lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.85,0:52:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel we're alike in some ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.42,0:52:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that we're both good at soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.86,0:52:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems unlikely. - Likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.73,0:52:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are really getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.73,0:52:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.23,0:52:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, be careful with the tea. - Watch that you don't burn yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.40,0:52:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, entertain Small B.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.84,0:52:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a cup of tea, Small B.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.51,0:52:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.91,0:53:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that another pal dropping by?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.21,0:53:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Just the garbage lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.95,0:53:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any trash to throw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.35,0:53:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She said the drain is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.99,0:53:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs to help you unblock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.79,0:53:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The drain is on the balcony, grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.79,0:53:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B, your voice is very familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.96,0:53:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have I heard it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.36,0:53:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.86,0:53:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't willing to sing the song I really liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.37,0:53:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Mr. Li. What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.50,0:53:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Small B. Why don't you tell Jenny a bit more about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.17,0:53:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to the toilet. - I need to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.94,0:53:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll lead the way. There's a toilet in my bedroom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.41,0:53:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's a big rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.68,0:53:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A rat again? - It's gone into the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.18,0:53:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I catch it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.91,0:54:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.08,0:54:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.39,0:54:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who is down there pointing a gun at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.58,0:54:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.01,0:54:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.38,0:54:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.05,0:54:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're both lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.79,0:54:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.72,0:54:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.33,0:54:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.73,0:54:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong is an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.43,0:55:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.87,0:55:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been after him for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.64,0:55:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.91,0:55:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, listen to me. - I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.01,0:55:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, don't be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.41,0:55:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, calm down. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.62,0:55:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.02,0:55:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong fired the shots that injured your eyes six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.36,0:55:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The triads want to silence him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.26,0:55:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.67,0:55:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The law cannot accommodate human folly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.58,0:55:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that you will cooperate with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.28,0:55:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...and help to lure him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.38,0:55:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.68,0:55:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.12,0:55:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ah Jong is in our custody, at least it will be to his benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.19,0:56:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than being killed by the triads.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.43,0:56:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how much it costs. I want him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.54,0:56:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He exposed his identity and broke the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.34,0:56:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him lying dead in front of my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.61,0:56:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,First transfer $100,000 into my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.71,0:56:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After the job is complete, add another $200,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.81,0:56:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't see the bank receipt,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.35,0:56:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,even if someone were to hold a gun to your head right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.78,0:56:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't move a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.02,0:56:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the bank now and take out the $100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.02,0:56:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. - Mr. Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.19,0:56:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finished. And you still have the guts to come see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.03,0:56:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should give him the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.06,0:56:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't give up until he gets his hands on his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.33,0:56:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? Is he going to shoot me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.14,0:56:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got brothers all over the streets. We'll see what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.51,0:56:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As a triad member, being trustworthy is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.38,0:56:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't beg. My decision is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.38,0:56:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Hoi, why can't you see this as a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.88,0:57:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...for me to fix things with a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.12,0:57:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That way things will be sorted out between us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.66,0:57:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Hoi,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.26,0:57:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kneel down... if it makes you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.20,0:57:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.97,0:57:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't a triad elder, I'd beat you senseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.87,0:57:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so special about him? He's just an insignificant nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.74,0:57:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't get it! Why are you on his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.58,0:57:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a complicated man.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.68,0:57:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.86,0:58:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happened! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.71,0:58:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.48,0:58:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.59,0:58:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, you're injured! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.15,0:58:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.39,0:58:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We can handle this! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.59,0:58:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.69,0:58:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.56,0:59:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still consider me a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.96,0:59:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then blow me away with one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.60,0:59:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see a friend kneeling in front of someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.33,0:59:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...begging to get me my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.07,0:59:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be very involved these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.57,0:59:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I always come through one my promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.74,0:59:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could kill you with one bullet,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.28,0:59:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then I wouldn't have to kneel in front of people and beg.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.28,0:59:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm ashamed of myself!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.81,1:00:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.91,1:00:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are no longer suited to the triad lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.78,1:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're too nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.59,1:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're the lucky ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.80,1:00:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes to die,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.43,1:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to leave without even one friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.93,1:00:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My only regret is that I owe you what was promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.55,1:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One can't think like that with friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.35,1:00:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, what are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.95,1:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.33,1:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.53,1:01:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny keeps hoping that she'll see the sea and sky again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.47,1:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done so much for her. I wonder how she feels about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.55,1:01:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. - Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.15,1:02:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong, why did you leave me so suddenly all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.49,1:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.59,1:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.99,1:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to leave tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.09,1:02:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.39,1:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ho contacted me and told me...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.96,1:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's a pair of corneas in Singapore...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.30,1:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...that lots of people are trying to get ahold of.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.40,1:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's reserved them for me,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.80,1:02:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and said that it would be best to leave tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.67,1:02:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.27,1:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've booked tickets for tonight. I'll wait for you at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.88,1:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to come tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.31,1:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.82,1:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'll come?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.39,1:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.70,1:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's never lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.78,1:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? - Let's check out that way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.98,1:03:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on all exits and corridors.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.49,1:03:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay alert, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.16,1:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all set up, unless he's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.26,1:03:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If he does come, he won't be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.49,1:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, please don't worry while you're away.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.19,1:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it up to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.26,1:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If something unusual happens, we will contact you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.89,1:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for seeing me off.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.06,1:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a good journey!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.53,1:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the company in your capable hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.24,1:04:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.41,1:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.84,1:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.15,1:04:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come! Ah Jong, run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.15,1:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. - What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.42,1:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Ah Jong! - Take care and have a safe journey!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.92,1:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many policemen here! Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.59,1:04:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.83,1:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The police want to arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.43,1:04:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.66,1:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.80,1:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! If you're here, run away.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.47,1:04:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly! Don't let them catch you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.08,1:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, are you waiting for someone? - Ah Jong! Run away! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.52,1:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The police want to arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.39,1:04:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.40,1:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Don't let them catch you!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.20,1:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Don't let them catch you!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.84,1:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.04,1:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.51,1:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.71,1:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.91,1:05:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.28,1:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.68,1:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.85,1:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, cop?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.02,1:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a crime to talk to a girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.10,1:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.36,1:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies! Apologies!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.89,1:05:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Search the area!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.03,1:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.03,1:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Checking out girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.00,1:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your profession?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.46,1:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a talent scout for a film company.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.60,1:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you fight my officers? - I was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.91,1:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunk?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.01,1:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up and walk a few steps!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.86,1:06:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.29,1:06:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.70,1:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you people live your life by a code of honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.83,1:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd want a friend like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.54,1:06:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you help me, you'll be helping him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.41,1:06:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not hindering him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.31,1:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help him resolve his situation,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.78,1:06:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which would also solve my problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.38,1:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to sort out your own problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.92,1:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If the person you're speaking of really doesn't have any friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.02,1:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then he would also have to resolve the situation himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.43,1:07:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Ying, from this moment onwards,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.03,1:07:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chan Bok Man will be in charge of your case.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.83,1:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been transferred to another case.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.14,1:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.34,1:07:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have confidence in you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.01,1:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your emotions are getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.48,1:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't succeed. You'll fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.35,1:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Inspector Dou, you've never understood me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.25,1:07:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I misunderstood you. That's why I'm replacing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.36,1:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up! - How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.63,1:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Tsang! Help Inspector Chan finish this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.16,1:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.37,1:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Release Fung immediately and then follow him around 24 hours a day...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.67,1:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...until you get some dirt on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.17,1:07:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.98,1:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.72,1:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,BE FILLED WITH HONOR
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.73,1:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you ever kill people again?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.60,1:08:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought I would only kill bad people, and not good people.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.61,1:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.02,1:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kill anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.65,1:08:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can achieve that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.48,1:11:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was followed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.82,1:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The cops and Wong Hoi's guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.95,1:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I managed to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.62,1:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wong Hoi hired a gang of experts to deal with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.96,1:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be okay. There are enough guns here for you to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.10,1:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.80,1:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get your money back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.47,1:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me at the church tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.88,1:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.04,1:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.11,1:12:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.15,1:12:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a triad elder.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.22,1:12:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to show me respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.15,1:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sei.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.02,1:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not possible, let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.63,1:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose a friend like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.44,1:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsang Yeh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.05,1:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I followed him to...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.35,1:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...number 6 Horizon Drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.06,1:13:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.09,1:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find it. - Horizon Drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.26,1:13:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.93,1:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find the place. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.60,1:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Ying...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.70,1:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about winning or losing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.61,1:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can win against everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.01,1:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes losing doesn't mean that you failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.95,1:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsang Yeh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.25,1:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsang Yeh!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.07,1:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Ying! Did he tell you where the assassin was?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.84,1:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ask him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.39,1:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.56,1:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.83,1:15:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.73,1:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong, why is it so dark?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.57,1:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's going to rain today.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.57,1:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Your eyes are fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.98,1:15:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we leaving now? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.08,1:15:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand still.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.08,1:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.22,1:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Small B. - Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.39,1:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's seeing us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.76,1:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you shot me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.83,1:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a policeman. I won't shoot someone in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.30,1:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the same rule in my profession. - They're nothing like each other!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.00,1:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I uphold the law, you violate it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.11,1:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't arrest you today,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.11,1:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how am I supposed to avenge my dead friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.31,1:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.52,1:16:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.19,1:16:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need to avenge your friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.76,1:16:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you just shoot me dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.12,1:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force me to fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.81,1:16:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you actually shot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.28,1:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't miss an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.95,1:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have many more.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.68,1:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.88,1:17:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.09,1:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B? Where is Small B?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.69,1:17:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.36,1:17:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't arrest him. - Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.69,1:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised me he won't kill anyone else again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.83,1:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down the gun first. Put down the gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.03,1:17:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let go of the gun unless you let us leave!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.50,1:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.40,1:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.18,1:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hit him? Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.81,1:17:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.21,1:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn't want to shoot him! - He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.08,1:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.89,1:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.19,1:18:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid! Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.22,1:18:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Ah Jong! - Don't go outside!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.98,1:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to arrest me, then we'll need to shoot our way out together!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.99,1:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss this after we get Jenny out safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.36,1:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My car is outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.23,1:19:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.24,1:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you take me back to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.94,1:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your gun down.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.28,1:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you won't kill a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.20,1:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.50,1:21:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have shot me dead with one bullet just now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.20,1:21:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't casually kill my enemy until I understand him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.91,1:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.81,1:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have guessed that the person who understood me...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.62,1:21:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...would be a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.42,1:22:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you could give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.29,1:22:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've considered that...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.06,1:22:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if I promise to do something, I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.03,1:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be as carefree.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.10,1:22:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I really want to do something, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.13,1:22:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in justice, but no one believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.94,1:22:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good people are usually misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.74,1:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't look like a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.85,1:22:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like an assassin either.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.95,1:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.05,1:22:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dragged you into all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.55,1:22:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know who's behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.39,1:22:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every profession has its rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.86,1:22:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.86,1:22:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.46,1:22:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the road you're taking is a long one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.20,1:22:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You must always take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.47,1:22:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have to arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.38,1:23:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.19,1:23:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.69,1:23:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When my friend brings me the cash,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.73,1:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll fly off to America tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.30,1:23:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those people will find us here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.70,1:23:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.24,1:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.51,1:23:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How come there isn't any light?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.51,1:23:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.85,1:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong, quickly turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.85,1:23:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you turn on the lights?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.23,1:23:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.34,1:23:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong, turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.67,1:24:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a temporary power failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.85,1:24:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your friend really going to show up?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.15,1:24:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He will.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.32,1:24:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He will. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.46,1:24:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, the money for Paul has already been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.06,1:24:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he can deal with Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.98,1:24:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, Brother Fung is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.58,1:24:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he betrays you again?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.82,1:24:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will still consider him a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.06,1:24:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he's helped me before.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.30,1:25:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the money. - Where's Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.00,1:25:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are few people who can be considered true friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.24,1:25:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They exist. They're just rare.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.89,1:25:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.96,1:25:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, throw down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.76,1:25:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your hand was damaged?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.16,1:25:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, but I still have some of the old pro left in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.17,1:25:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your profession only leads to death. Why continue with it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.90,1:25:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach me how to retrace my steps then.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.81,1:25:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my money?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.18,1:25:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Sing!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.86,1:26:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.19,1:26:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have shot me in the head!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.53,1:26:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.30,1:26:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't held a gun in so long. I'm less competent now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.40,1:26:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a chance, I'd restart my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.21,1:26:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.68,1:26:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that money.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.75,1:26:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.25,1:26:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should give him that money.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.49,1:26:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the meaning of ethics and honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.22,1:26:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.36,1:26:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ethics and honor valid in your profession?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.57,1:26:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.67,1:26:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people believe in the old values.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.44,1:26:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, if it's this tough for you being human,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.78,1:26:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better for you to be a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.25,1:26:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually we're very similar.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.05,1:27:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We both make a living with our guns.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.19,1:27:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But how we use our guns is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.52,1:27:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.06,1:27:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be a dog, but I still have my dignity.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.94,1:27:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't tell me where Ah Jong is,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.61,1:27:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't even get the chance to be a dog!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.08,1:27:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw him in the garbage!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.30,1:27:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me the money!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.40,1:27:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have any bullets?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.04,1:27:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.54,1:27:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of us in our profession...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.51,1:27:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...usually save the last bullet...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.64,1:28:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...to kill someone else or kill ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.66,1:28:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.20,1:28:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.41,1:28:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I miscounted. I'm a failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.95,1:28:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow him! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.65,1:28:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.86,1:28:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm killed but my eyes aren't injured...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.43,1:28:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...get me to a hospital and save my corneas for Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.43,1:28:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.64,1:29:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,then give her the money and get her on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.64,1:29:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there no other choices?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.51,1:29:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time in my life that I've done the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.05,1:29:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to help me?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.52,1:29:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.19,1:29:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone arrive? - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.24,1:30:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sei.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.91,1:30:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your money.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.08,1:30:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the money for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.05,1:30:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to be able to settle matters for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.56,1:30:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sei. Thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.77,1:30:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.78,1:30:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.98,1:30:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if I'm a man or a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.12,1:30:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sei, they have no right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.62,1:30:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sei! Brother Sei!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.67,1:31:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sei...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.74,1:31:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm just a dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.05,1:31:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.25,1:31:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.08,1:31:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are no longer suited for this kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.59,1:31:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be put down like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.33,1:31:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.60,1:31:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dying, and I don't even have my last bullet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.27,1:31:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.01,1:31:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.55,1:32:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong. - Stay here and don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.65,1:32:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.25,1:32:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.72,1:32:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to shoot our way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.96,1:32:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't kill any more people.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.26,1:32:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down your gun and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.76,1:32:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down my gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.76,1:32:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had to kill my oldest friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.97,1:32:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're asking me to throw down my gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.17,1:32:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When my partner died, I wanted to shoot you, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.37,1:32:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I don't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.98,1:33:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Jenny and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.38,1:33:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.22,1:33:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I run to the ends of the earth, they'll still follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.58,1:33:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run away. I'm ending this here!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.39,1:33:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go outside and try telling them that you're a cop!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.59,1:33:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if they drop their weapons!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.31,1:33:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny. - Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.42,1:33:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.43,1:34:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B! - Thanks, Shrimp Head!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.52,1:34:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B, I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.86,1:34:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about favors.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.86,1:34:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,One can never fully repay favors done out of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.06,1:35:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, don't run!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.40,1:35:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay there! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.01,1:35:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny! Jenny!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.66,1:37:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.00,1:37:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.03,1:37:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head! Catch!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.49,1:37:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a good shot?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.16,1:37:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How else could I be a cop?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.23,1:38:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After being friends for so long,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.23,1:38:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know your real name.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.20,1:38:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.17,1:38:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me that after all this is settled,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.60,1:38:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not dead, you'll have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.94,1:38:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be nice to be able to remember I once had you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.27,1:38:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you want me to die or escape?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.21,1:38:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If fate hasn't already decided, then I don't want either.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.05,1:38:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you care about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.42,1:38:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you nickname me Shrimp Head?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.91,1:39:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are my friends?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.01,1:39:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hurt her!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.28,1:39:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk! Walk!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.60,1:40:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.80,1:40:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to throw down your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.90,1:40:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, will you or won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.90,1:40:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.24,1:40:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Ah Jong?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.17,1:40:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.64,1:40:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.61,1:40:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You had better put down your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.28,1:40:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny, don't struggle!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.09,1:40:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.62,1:40:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.42,1:40:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.23,1:40:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go! - Don't make any dumb moves!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.03,1:40:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the girl go first! - No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.24,1:40:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I don't let her go?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.25,1:40:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.46,1:41:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Small B...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.86,1:41:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're able to pull off what you promised me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.10,1:41:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.57,1:41:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you still have a friend to back you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.49,1:41:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not throwing down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.69,1:41:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill her if you don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.77,1:41:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it down, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.95,1:42:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.95,1:42:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.25,1:42:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.82,1:43:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.19,1:43:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.49,1:43:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.54,1:44:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Jong!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.95,1:44:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.06,1:44:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender! I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.42,1:44:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to cooperate with the police!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.83,1:44:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock me up!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.60,1:44:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't look like a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.40,1:44:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like an assassin either.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.60,1:44:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in justice, but no one believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.97,1:44:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good people are usually misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.88,1:44:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest him! - Let me!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.31,1:44:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest me! Arrest me! Take me away!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.62,1:44:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I request police protection!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.02,1:44:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will cooperate...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.51,1:45:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.11,1:45:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.62,1:45:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrimp Head...
